mal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系<span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　</span>助理研究员<br><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">● </span>2018.01 – 2020.01<span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系<span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　</span>博士后<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,microsoft yahei; font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">主要从事深地前沿先进探测方法研究、暗物质直接探测和无中微子双贝塔衰变实验研究。具体包括：<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br>（1）高纯锗探测器的关键性能研究，主要是指在地下实验室低本底条件下的性能研究，如能量刻度、物理阈值、分辨率、死层厚度及均匀性等；<br>（2）高纯锗阵列实验系统液氮环境下的刻度方法、数据分析方法、探测器模拟、波形甄别、本底抑制方法等研究；<br>（3）暗物质直接探测和无中微子双贝塔衰变实验中的数据分析、物理分析等；<br>（4）超出标准模型新物理研究。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">参与合作团队：<br>（1）中国暗物质实验（CDEX）合作组：在中国锦屏地下实验室使用高纯锗探测器阵列进行暗物质直接探测和无中微子双贝塔衰变实验研究。<br>（2）PIRE-GEMADARC合作组：旨在针对暗物质探测、无中微子双贝塔衰变等稀有物理事例实验，开发高纯锗探测器新技术。<br>（3） LEGEND合作组：高纯锗阵列无中微子双贝塔衰变实验，LEGEND 吨级实验的物理目标是达到约10 meV的有效中微子质量探测灵敏度，具备确定中微子质量顺序的能力。</span><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span> 2024/01-2026/12，高纯锗探测器稀有事例探测实验，国家自然科学基金优秀青年科学基金，负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span> 2022/12-2027/11，利用极低阈值高纯锗探测器测量反应堆中微子-原子核相干散射过程，国家重点研发计划青年科学家项目，负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span> 2021/01-2023/12，Ge-76无中微子双贝塔衰变实验中的alpha本底研究，国家自然科学基金青年基金项目，负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span> 2022/01-2025.12，液氮屏蔽百公斤级 Ge-76无中微子双贝塔衰变实验辐射本底研究，国家自然科学基金面上项目，主要参与人。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span><br></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br></span></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; text-align: justify; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">详见：<a href=\"https://thurid.lib.tsinghua.edu.cn/scholar/23663772\" target=\"_blank\">https://thurid.lib.tsinghua.edu.cn/scholar/23663772</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1.&nbsp; Z. Y. Zhang, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Experimental Limits on Solar Reflected Dark Matter with a New Approach on Accelerated-Dark-Matter–Electron Analysis in Semiconductors. Physical Review Letters 132(17): 171001 (2024).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2.&nbsp; Z. Y. Zhang, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Constraints on Sub-GeV Dark Matter– Electron Scattering from the CDEX-10 Experiment, Physical Review Letters 129(22): 221301 (2022).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3.&nbsp; R. Xu, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Constraints on sub-GeV dark matter boosted by cosmic rays from the CDEX-10 experiment at the China Jinping Underground Laboratory, Physical Review D 106(5): 052008 (2022).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4.&nbsp; Z. Z. Liu, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Studies of the Earth shielding effect to direct dark matter searches at the China Jinping Underground Laboratory, Physical Review D 105(5): 052005 (2022).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">5.&nbsp; Z. She#, L. P. Jia#, Q. Yue*, …, L. T. Yang*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Direct Detection Constraints on Dark Photons with the CDEX-10 Experiment at the China Jinping Underground Laboratory, Physical Review Letters 124(11): 111301 (2020).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">6.&nbsp; Z. H. Zhang, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Probing dark matter particles from evaporating primordial black holes via electron scattering in the CDEX-10 experiment, Science China - Physics, Mechanics &amp; Astronomy 67(10): 101011 (2024).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">7.&nbsp; X. P. Geng, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Projected WIMP sensitivity of the CDEX-50 dark matter experiment, Journal of Cosmology and Astroparticle Physics 07: 009 (2024).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">8.&nbsp; B. T. Zhang#, J. Z. Wang#, L. T. Yang*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Searching for 76Ge neutrinoless double beta decay with the CDEX-1B experiment, Chinese Physics C 48(10): 101001 (2024).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">9.&nbsp; L. T. Yang*, R. Xu, Q. Yue. Recent Status and Prospects of CDEX dark matter search at CJPL, Proceedings of Science PoS(TAUP2023)051.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">10.&nbsp; L. T. Yang*, Y. F. Liang, Q. Yue. RECODE program for reactor neutrino CEvNS detection with PPC Germanium detector, Proceedings of Science PoS(TAUP2023)296.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">11.&nbsp; Z. H. Zhang, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Search for boosted keV-MeV light dark matter particles from evaporating primordial black holes at the CDEX-10 experiment, Physical Review D 108(5): 052006 (2023).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">12.&nbsp; Wang, Yufeng; Liu, Jiaxuan*; Yang, Litao*; Zeng, Zhi; Ma, Hao; Yue, Qian. Rare physical events at China Jinping underground laboratory (中国锦屏地下实验室与稀有物理实验), Nuclear Techniques (核技术) 46(8): 170-178 (2023).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">13.&nbsp; X. P. Geng, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Search for exotic interactions of solar neutrinos in the CDEX-10 experiment, Physical Review D 107(11): 112002 (2023).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">14.&nbsp; J. W. Hu, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue, X. P. Geng, H. B. Li, Y. F. Liang, S. T. Lin, S. K. Liu, H. Ma, L. Wang, H. T. Wong, B. T. Zhang. Measurement of the Compton scattering in germanium with a p-type point- contact germanium detector for dark matter detection, Journal of Instrumentation 18: P04011 (2023).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">15.&nbsp; 程建平, 柳卫平, 岳骞*, 李会红, 董国轩, 刘江来, 何建军, 郭冰, 杨丽桃*. 深地前沿物理研究中的关键科学问题. 中国科学基金. 2022年第36卷第3期，447-459页.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">16.&nbsp; Y. Wang, Z. Zeng, Q. Yue*, L. T. Yang*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). First experimental constraints on WIMP couplings in the effective field theory framework from CDEX, Science China - Physics, Mechanics &amp; Astronomy 64(8): 281011 (2021).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">17.&nbsp; Catarina Cosme*, Maíra Dutra*, Teng Ma*, Yongcheng Wu*, Litao Yang*. Neutrino portal to FIMP dark matter with an early matter era, Journal of High Energy Physics 03: 026 (2021).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">18.&nbsp; 岳骞, 马豪, 田阳, 杨丽桃, 刘仲智, 佘泽, 张炳韬, 张震宇. 无中微子双贝塔衰变实验, 北京：科学出版社, 2020.10// 第四章 Ge-76无中微子双贝塔衰变实验.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">19. 杨丽桃, 刘书魁*, 岳骞*. 中国暗物质实验研究进展. 中国基础科学, 136(04): 14-21+64.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">20.&nbsp; L. T. Yang#, H. B. Li#, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Search for Light Weakly-Interacting - Massive-Particle Dark Matter by Annual Modulation Analysis with a Point-Contact Germanium Detector at the China Jinping Underground Laboratory, Physical Review Letters 123(22): 221301 (2019).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">21.&nbsp; Z. Z. Liu, Q. Yue*, L. T. Yang*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Constraints on Spin-Independent Nucleus Scattering with Sub-GeV Weakly Interacting Massive Particle Dark Matter from the CDEX-1B Experiment at the China Jinping Underground Laboratory, Physical Review Letters 123(16): 161301 (2019).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">22.&nbsp; Yang L T*, Ma H, Yue Q. The CDEX-10 Experiment at the China Jinping Underground Laboratory: The First Results on Light WIMP Searches，亚太物理学会会刊AAPPS Bulletin 28(05): 31-34 (2018).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">23.&nbsp; H. Jiang, L. T. Yang*, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Performances of a prototype point- contact germanium detector immersed in liquid nitrogen for light dark matter search, Science China - Physics, Mechanics &amp; Astronomy 62(3): 031012 (2019).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">24.&nbsp; H. Jiang#, L. P. Jia#, Q. Yue*, …, L. T. Yang*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Limits on Light Weakly Interacting Massive Particles from the First 102.8 kg × day Data of the CDEX-10 Experiment, Physical Review Letters 120(24): 241301 (2018).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">25.&nbsp; L. T. Yang, H. B. Li, Q. Yue*, et al, (CDEX Collaboration). Limits on light WIMPs with a 1 kg-scale germanium detector at 160 eVee physics threshold at the China Jinping Underground Laboratory, Chinese Physics C 42(2): 023002 (2018).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">26.&nbsp; L. T. Yang, H. B. Li*, H. T. Wong, M. Agartioglu, J. H. Chen, L. P. Jia, H. Jiang, J. Li, F. K. Lin, S. T. Lin, S. K. Liu, J. L. Ma, B. Sevda, V. Sharma, L. Singh, M. K. Singh, M. K. Singh, A. K. Soma, A. Sonay, S. W. Yang, L. Wang, Q. Wang, Q. Yue*, W. Zhao. Bulk and surface event identification in p-type germanium detectors, Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research Section A 886: 13-23 (2018).</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; text-align: justify; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">●&nbsp;2024.02<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\"> – </span>至今 &nbsp;《核技术》期刊 &nbsp;青年编委</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2019.11 – 2020.11 PIRE-GEMADARC合作组指导委员会青年委员</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>                 \n    \n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    <div class=\"links-box\">\n        <div class=\"links\">\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:20px;\"></div>\n            <div class=\"model-title\">\n                <div class=\"model\">常用链接</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"model-block\"></div>\n            <ul>\n      <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74493)\"><li>清华大学</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://news.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74494)\"><li>清华新闻网</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://tsinghua.cn.libguides.com/c.php?g=91